{"tid":1693372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有關全民三罷] 我地入左囚徒困境喇知嘛？","createTime":"2019-11-04T14:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T11:23:32.000Z","uid":303210,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2b4e7063cb4d07ceaf6d954f78658893c76b6b","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無聽過囚徒困境呢個經濟學理論。<br />\n<br />\n要罷工成功一定要全世界參與先得，如果唔係政府唔會跪。<br />\n<br />\n但過往五個月以黎，我地每次罷工都失敗（Sorry我唔當8.5係成功因為政府根本無跪）係因為我地落入<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">囚徒困境</span></span>個trap<br />\n<br />\n我嘗試試分析俾大家睇：<br />\n而家有兩堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋有有罷工同埋唔罷工嘅選擇，<br />\n啫係話我地會出現4個情況：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷、<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔罷：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被炒、被清算，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無事，安然渡過<br />\n結果: 罷工無影響力，政府依然無跪，全世界輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔罷、<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無事，安然渡過，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被炒、被清算<br />\n結果: 罷工無影響力，政府依然無跪，全世界輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔罷、<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔罷:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無事，安然渡過，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無事，安然渡過<br />\n結果: 政府安然無恙，五大訴求依然未得回應，全世界輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷、<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能會被炒，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能會被炒<br />\n結果: 整個香港停擺，港府在壓力底下會被逼回應5大訴求，運動正式結束，香港人勝利<br />\n<br />\n我地咁樣分析得知，雙方彼此合作、罷工可為全體帶來最佳利益（整個香港停擺，港府在壓力底下會被逼回應5大訴求，運動正式結束，香港人勝利)，但在無法溝通的情況下，因為出賣同夥可為自己帶來利益（無事，安然渡過)(雖然有溝通最後亦會有機會食言），所以人會理性地選擇出賣對方。<br />\n<br />\n透過囚徒困境嘅分析，我覺得好心up。<br />\n因為之前每次所謂大罷工都失敗，話俾我聽嘅係，香港人話過齊上齊落，原來係得個講，有人最後都係出賣左其他人。<br />\n<br />\n一個群體中，個人做出理性選擇卻往往導致集體的非理性。<br />\n<br />\n所以，香港人，要點揀，我諗你地知嘅！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷佢老母啦好嘛！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e06a7f6c4e4173843b49b55f8bc3ffe3a88a6ed8","tid":1693372,"uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要一齊先有用"},{"pid":"ca1d564fa7fdd158593f027ee6fb8c5e1cab06b5","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06a7f6c4e4173843b49b55f8bc3ffe3a88a6ed8","tid":1693372,"uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要一齊先有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"係，無錯<br />\n<br />\n要打破困境"},{"pid":"d58197a53cc235e0932e4ad57329142eff946c88","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"自推先"},{"pid":"cb77df180ac452fa0eae9d4c4d88a8cbfe48c5f6","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"雖然P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"8d30d8e1081ddb85e9fd010e3ac3f432de9c0217","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"但我想大家睇到"},{"pid":"132614f1d3956fcdd176dc66412be2bbcedb0410","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"推上熱門！"},{"pid":"489c35f23b1cbde966d4515f53cd437df64da71f","tid":1693372,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"